ind this easier, and a handy 3kg claim will offset his weight rise. Stick with him on an each-way basis. 6. LADY ZAYDI came from last and was only beaten 2 lengths over 1200m at Eagle Farm 17 days ago. She benefits from a 2kg claim, and with the long run in on this track with an extra 200m, she can figure in the top 3. 8. TRUSTY BANDIT dropped back to this trip at Dalby, and finished all over the top of his rivals to score by nearly a length. This is a tougher assignment, but he drops sharply in weight, and that makes him a top 4 player again.\",\"runners\":[2,1,6,8],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Russell Leonard","tipRunnerNumbers":[2,1,8,6]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,6,1,8]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,5,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,2,4,7]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,6,7]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,6,4,1]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,2,1,7]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}}]}}}